docs.name: Zillow Home Value Index: All Homes - Washington
docs.description: The Zillow Home Value Index is the median Zestimate valuation for a given geographic area on a given day. A Zestimate is Zillow's estimate of the current market value for a home. We have tens of millions of Zestimates - one for most homes. Our data is refreshed regularly to reflect real estate transactions that could affect you - even if you're not buying or selling a house.

docs.name: Zillow Home Value Index (Cities): Single Family Residence - Long Lake, MN
docs.description: The Zillow Home Value Index is Zillow's estimate of the median market value of single family residences within the city of Long Lake, MN. This data is calculated by Zillow Real Estate Research (www.zillow.com/research) using their database of 110 million homes.

docs.name: Zillow Home Value Index (Zip Codes): Middle Tier Homes - 97471,Roseburg,OR
docs.description: The Zillow Home Value Index is Zillow's estimate of the median market value of middle tier homes within the zip code of 97471, Roseburg, OR. Middle tier homes are homes that fall into the middle third of home values within the region. This data is calculated by Zillow Real Estate Research (www.zillow.com/research) using their database of 110 million homes.

docs.name: Zillow Metrics (Zip Codes): Sale-to-List Price Ratio - 98022,Enumclaw,WA
docs.description: Median of the ratio between the sale price and the list price for all homes (e.g. if a home with a list price of $200k sells for $250k, its ratio would be 5:4 or 1.25). This data is calculated by Zillow Real Estate Research (www.zillow.com/research) using their database of 110 million homes.

docs.name: Zillow Home Value Index (Zip Codes): Median Value Per Sq. Ft. (All Homes) - 97131,Nehalem,OR
docs.description: The Zillow Home Value Index is Zillow's estimate of the median market value of all homes within the zip code of 97131, Nehalem, OR. This number is derived by taking the estimated home value for each home and dividing it by the homes square footage. This data is calculated by Zillow Real Estate Research (www.zillow.com/research) using their database of 110 million homes.
